        ncautoscale
        ncbyte
        ncchar
        ncdouble
        ncdump
        ncfloat
        ncint
        nclong
        ncshort
        netcdf_setup
        ncatt
        ncclose
        ncdatatype
        ncdim
        ncenddef
        ncname
        ncredef
        ncsync
        ncvar
        netcdf
        ncisrecord
Examples:
        example_netcdf
        example_opendap
<<

